Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.83,0:00:06.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:22.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:24.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:28.29,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:29.76,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:36.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:44.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:53.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:01:00.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:07.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:13.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:22.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:26.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:39.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...\nslippers, detergent, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:42.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I forgot to get clothespins!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:46.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of extra clothespins\nat the temple. You're welcome to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:52.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Living on your own is more\nexpensive than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:57.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you move in with Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm finally moving to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:02.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to enjoy\nsingle life to the fullest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:06.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I don't want to get\nin the way of you two... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:13.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's right, it's White Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.06,0:02:15.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you already get\nsomething from Kei today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:16.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:21.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A return gift for the chocolates. I bet he\ngave something neutral like cookies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:24.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolates, did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:28.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, you didn't know about\NValentine's Day last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.98,0:02:29.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:32.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:44.81,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Where to Confess One's Love?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:49.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? You practice such\ncustoms here on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:53.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say ''on Earth''...\nIt's more like ''in Japan.''
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:57.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But in a relationship like yours, giving\NKei chocolates would be a no-brainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:03:01.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi, did you offer a\ngift to someone as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:05.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, because I don't care\nabout that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Kei might be\ntaking it a little hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Has he been acting\nstrangely at all recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Another sunny day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}\NAnother sunny day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:23.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the 2nd week of February.\NSpring is right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:30.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you know about any\nof the customs we have here on Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am familiar with several of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:47.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What day is it today again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it's Monday,\nthen that means... right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must be the 14th. I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}\NOh, I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:04.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The 14th is the day the Auto Club\npresents its monthly expense report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:14.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, he was {\i1}so{\i0} waiting for it,\nwasn't he!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:18.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really have a good\ngrasp on the customs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.62,0:04:23.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you guys are living together...\nyou can't blame him for being depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:28.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Megumi, I didn't\nknow you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We should be heading for school soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll go get ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.97,0:04:33.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:39.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go somewhere with Belldandy\ntoday, so you go on ahead to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:51.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I think I'll go and\napologize to Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:55.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize, it'll make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}\NDon't apologize, it'll make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:00.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a better idea.\NJust do what I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:16.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let this mouth-watering\nchocolate be suffused with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:19.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my feelings for\NKeiichi as his goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:24.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and make up for my not\nhaving given it to him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:31.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No question about it,\NKei's gonna be thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really look happy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:42.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's my reason for being here...\nto make Keiichi happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:46.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad... that you're\nthe woman in Kei's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:51.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now all you have to do is take Kei\nto a romantic spot and hand it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And tell him, ''Sorry I was late!''
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And that will fix everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:08.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man... it's March already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:14.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, weren't you\ngoing out with Megumi today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:19.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... actually, I have\nsomething for you, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:21.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:25.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to give me that ugly bouquet\nin an unromantic place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How insensitive are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unromantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:35.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take him to a romantic spot\nand hand it to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:38.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you'd call\nan unromantic place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:43.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, I guess most\npeople would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:46.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:46.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, wait! Belldandy!{\i0}\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, wait! Belldandy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:54.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really! These days you can throw a\nrock and hit 10 clueless guys like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:07:00.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you! What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:04.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you could tell me\nwhere I can find a ''romantic spot.''
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Romantic...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:11.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I have to give Keiichi\nthese chocolates in a romantic place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Being sarcastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:14.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:20.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're just gushing over Morisato like\nthat to make me give up on him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on him? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:25.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you playing dumb again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:26.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Playing dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:32.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute... is this girl just naive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... so can you tell me about the spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A romantic spot, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:42.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to tell me\nwhere I can find one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:45.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure I'll tell you, but in return,\nI want you to meow like a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:50.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stick your head outside\nand shout ''Yahoo!''
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:53.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:53.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No question about it now...{\i0}\NYahoo! Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:59.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:00.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:06.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So he's going to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here he comes! That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:18.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone knows about\nromantic spots, it's that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:28.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who that guy is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:31.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The No. 1 Casanova on campus...\NToshiyuki Aoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:34.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you approach him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:39.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please tell me where\nI can find a ''romantic spot''?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:47.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Both her body and looks make the\ngrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess today's my lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:52.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Let's go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:59.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Come back! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:05.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you're in that rogue's clutches\nhe'll have his way with you, and once...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:10.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the rumors start to fly, you'll\nnever want to show your face here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Belldandy went on home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:22.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She sure was acting kind of weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:32.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why did it have to die\non me at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that\nthis is a romantic spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would Keiichi really be happy if\nI brought him to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, can you\nthink of another place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:58.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:02.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I don't think Keiichi\nwould like it if I brought him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:06.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who gives a damn about a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you here because\nI wanted to make you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:13.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that won't do...\nthe goal is to make Keiichi happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:20.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean that jerk is\nactually forcing you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, he's not forcing me at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:27.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely why I want\NKeiichi to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:33.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what your motive was, but\nthe fact is that you came here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:38.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NYou know perfectly well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:44.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running? You're the one\nwho pretty much said you wanted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:46.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never said such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:50.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little late to say no!\nI want you to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've hit a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Run, O Spirit of Lightning,\nrelease yourself from your shackles...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And subject this man to an ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:02.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what kind of spell...{\i0}\NAnd subject this man to an ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what kind of spell...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:07.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy! Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:53.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm gonna change now,\nso you stay out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.21,0:11:54.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear a word I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:59.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That guy duped her into\ngoing with him, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:03.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's from another country. She doesn't\nknow how things are done in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\nI guess it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:06.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:13.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You went along with him to find\na romantic spot, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.29,0:12:18.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:22.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... could you tell me?\NWhere a romantic spot might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:24.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I could do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:28.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make Keiichi\nhappy, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:35.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, you're such a lucky dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:56.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Senior, I can't do it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:57.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:03.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I wanted to ask you if\nyou had any plans for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:07.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, I'm not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there's someplace I'd like to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:13.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you'd\naccompany me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:21.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then please come to the living room\nafter you've gotten dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:28.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now all you have to do is\ntake him to places he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:29.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:33.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing is, I'm not really sure\nwhat kind of place he'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:39.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you go with him, he'll have\na ball no matter where you take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won them in the\nprize-drawing at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you take him there, I guarantee\nhe'll have himself a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:51.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing, you two have\nto be alone together, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:52.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Three's a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:54.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:57.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought the more the merrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:14:00.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because then it won't\nbe fun for him anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's how he'd feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:06.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, trust me!\NThat's how any guy would feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:20.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someplace she'd like to go? I wonder\nwhat's up with her, all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:29.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had much time to be alone\nlately, so I guess it's good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:36.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you wanted to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:37.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:41.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd have a good time\nif we came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did? Well, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:46.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go, but I didn't have\nthe money so I'd given up on the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:53.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!\NThanks so much, Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:01.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd shadow them, but it looks\nlike there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:05.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this is the last place\nanyone would call romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:18.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what Megumi was\ntalking about... a ''romantic spot''!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:28.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All righty, I guess it's time\nfor the third wheel to back out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go look at the stuff over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}\NWanna go look at the stuff over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:41.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh, what can I do\nto distract those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:47.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! I just touched it\nand the whole thing broke off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is where you and I come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.35,0:15:54.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can just leave that to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It just so happens, we're\nfrom the NIT Auto Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's the Seniors?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:04.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, I forgot, Kei's\na member of the Auto Club too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:05.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:09.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a shrine to those of us in\nthe Auto Club and you dare bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Belldandy here on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:14.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable! Now then,\nwhy don't you just come with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We must decline!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:20.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must spend the day alone\nwith Keiichi today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:21.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, shall we go, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:32.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think...\nshe doesn't like us anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's tougher than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:38.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no need for me\nto follow them anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I really had a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:51.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now why don't we go someplace\nwhere you can enjoy yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I must see to it that you\nhave a good time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:57.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:01.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...where would Keiichi have fun,\na fun place for Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! Come on, let's go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:17.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can fix cars to\nyour heart's content here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe I can, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not fun here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.74,0:17:24.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course it's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:32.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Such a variety of cars and motorcycles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No good either?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:41.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all these ancient cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:49.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I hardly ever get the\nchance to come to a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at this one, it's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:56.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So they used parts like these\nback in the old days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:02.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I really do appreciate\nall your concern for me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I think you're trying a little too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:09.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You seem somewhat blue these days...\NThat's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:14.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want you to always have\na smile on your face, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:21.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, there's a place I want to go.\NWill you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:42.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a ferry that's\nbeen around for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I like doing this...\ntaking the last boat at sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:48.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:53.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know what made you\nact the way you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:19:01.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you see, since I didn't give you\nchocolate for Valentine's Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:06.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't know the\ncustoms here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:14.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.\NHow can I call myself your goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:17.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...when I've made you feel so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:21.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were trying so\nhard to show me a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.59,0:19:28.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am a failure as a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!\nI had such a good time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:33.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you the truth.\nI mean, I had you by my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:41.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...laughing and looking so happy,\neven looking worried once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:44.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:47.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to fulfill\nmy job as a goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:50.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, I want you to take me\nto a place that you like, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:59.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what places\nyou like, Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:05.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To learn more about you...\nthere's nothing I'd enjoy more right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:17.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is my favorite place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where the wind crossing\nthe vast ocean meets...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the wind that has\ndescended from the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:29.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear so many different voices\nright here. It's such a lovely place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:39.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is it...\nthis is a ''romantic spot,'' isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:52.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:56.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for not\ngiving it to you sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.05,0:21:01.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:05.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's for you, in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:36.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:39.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it always end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:53.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you did give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:57.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:01.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:06.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong after all.\NCome to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:13.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The System Force has vanished, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:20.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then does all\nthis sneezing mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:49.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:59.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:05.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:12.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:15.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.31,0:23:21.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.23,0:23:27.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:33.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for you\ngives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.67,0:23:39.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:44.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:59.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Blood ties... connections made by\ndestiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:03.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A connection that's no different\neven if you happen to be goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:07.54,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! Can You Pass the\NLove Test With Those Low Scores?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:10.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are goddesses allowed\nto wear white lab coats?
